27 b. To renew a license, a licensed business entity public adjuster shall file a biennial
28 license continuation in the form and manner prescribed by the commissioner.
29 c. A business entity public adjuster license may be renewed within the ninety-day
30 period immediately preceding the expiration date upon payment of the renewal
31 fee, not to exceed one hundred fifty dollars, prescribed by the commissioner. A
